=> Types of Parameters in APIs

There are three main ways APIs receive data.

1️⃣ Path Parameters

Example:

/square/5

Here 5 is input to the API.

2️⃣ Query Parameters

Example:

/search?name=ashish
3️⃣ Request Body

Used in POST requests

Example:

{
 "name": "Ashish",
 "age": 21
}

We will use these later when sending ML data.




